-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-Usp6SjjMy8q7j454I2VFBw">Ngâm nguyệt kỳ 3 - 吟月其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/T%C3%A1i-phi%E1%BA%BFm-Ng%C3%B4-giang/poem-Syr0IjUXrF2nz9RUYNxm4g">Tái phiếm Ngô giang - 再泛吳江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-gsSbrX8mxDOHV8mbduxYMg">Vương Vũ Xứng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/V%E1%BB%8Dng-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai-Du-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-Uoy2mSjnk7btxI4Fq9Zp3A">Vọng Bồng Lai - Du hứng - 望蓬萊—遊興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/author-Xdrx9PY_HQVilIv5qP5QxQ">Khâu Xứ Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C5%A9-trung-qu%C3%A1-Th%E1%BA%A5t-L%C3%BD-lung-ca/poem-t1zljGkZZw_rj7vXYCTTVw">Vũ trung quá Thất Lý lung ca - 雨中過七里瀧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-T%C3%ADch-K%E1%BB%B3/author-leXS2a46kBYHa9AoDh5zfw">Ngô Tích Kỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
